REPORT ZRSA12_10.


DATA: gv_a TYPE i,
      gv_b LIKE gv_a,
      gv_r LIKE gv_b.

gv_a = 10.
gv_b = 20.

*Subroutine
PERFORM cal USING gv_a gv_b gv_r.


WRITE gv_r.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal USING VALUE(p_a)
               VALUE(p_b)
               VALUE(p_r).

gv_r = p_a + p_b.
ENDFORM.
